Deuterons were detected by three
deltaE-E telescopes. Totally depleted silicon surface
barrier detectors with the thickness of 200-250 mu-m
were used as deltaE detectors. E-detectors manufactured
by Li drift into silicon have a sensitive area of
3000-5500 mu-m. Total energy resolution was 1-1.5%.
